parameters: D-did you come to save me...!
Of course! Now, let's escape together.

No, I'm fine on my own. Instead, our comrades...
they must be going through something much worse.

I'll take care of supporting this person, Esuka,
you continue the search.
Damn it! I didn't make it in time!

Esuka, there are still comrades who have been
captured, we need to hurry.

She seems to have suffered a terrible torture...
she's barely breathing...

Damn... Have I been injected with some kind of
drug?

Shuu, you don't seem to be able to stand on your
own. I'll carry you and we'll escape!
Ah! You've come to help me!
Now, let's escape! Can you stand?

I'm afraid my leg is broken... Could you possibly
carry me?

...? What's wrong, Shuu? Is something bothering
you?

※A choice will appear after this. Do you want to
save? (Depending on your choice, it may result in
a game over)

Buhuhu! I did it! I, who was scorned as a failure,
have captured the Resistance!
Are you really with the Resistance?

Well, it can't be helped if I'm found out! Even
though I'm considered a failure, I'm still one of
the modified soldiers! Let's have a fair and
square fight! A fight!

I'm not quite sure what happened, but at least I'm
glad we didn't have to call for backup.

It seems they're conducting quite reckless
experiments to turn people into modified soldiers.
I suppose there are some who end up with issues in
their judgment and personality.
